Exceptions are stuff from which we can recover
It is in the throwable class and this class is inherited from the object class
It has two types Exception and Error
--> In Exception there are two types:
--> 1. CHECKED : Type in which the exception is found at compile time like FILE_NOTFOUND Error
--> 2. UNCHECKED : Type in which the exception is not found at compile time and is found when the program runs like DIVISION_BY_ZERO